</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>航拍機拍出南生圍日出地霧　夢幻相片公開火速吸 like</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/21/drone-hk/dc/photogism/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=drone-hk</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 21 Dec 2021 06:59:55 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[攝影文化]]></category><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[南生圍]]></category><category><![CDATA[日出地霧]]></category><category><![CDATA[航拍機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1077305</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>風景優美的南生圍一向都是航拍機的飛行聖地，近日有人拍的一個特別現象，相片僅上載數小時便火速吸引過 2,600  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>風景優美的南生圍一向都是航拍機的飛行聖地，近日有人拍的一個特別現象，相片僅上載數小時便火速吸引過 2,600 個 like。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6BFB49111996-1.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077309" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6BFB49111996-1-338x580.jpeg" alt="" width="338" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6BFB49111996-1-338x580.jpeg 338w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6BFB49111996-1-525x900.jpeg 525w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6BFB49111996-1-768x1317.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6BFB49111996-1-895x1536.jpeg 895w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6BFB49111996-1.jpeg 933w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 338px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲相片來源： <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/553511078046085/permalink/4977212165675932/">Facebook 群組「香港風景攝影會」</a></p><p>網名 Shun Wong 的樓主在 Facebook 群組「香港風景攝影會」分享了 3 張相，相片中的太陽剛從山上升起，晨曦漸露輝映著大地，而天上的雲不多，只數朵薄雲依稀可見。加上前方沒有高樓大廈的遮擋，令風景一覽無遺，甚至連遠方的山脈都清晰可見。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/267587012_10165813705855032_6465005238911365254_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077306" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/267587012_10165813705855032_6465005238911365254_n-694x396.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/267587012_10165813705855032_6465005238911365254_n-694x396.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/267587012_10165813705855032_6465005238911365254_n-1280x729.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/267587012_10165813705855032_6465005238911365254_n-768x438.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/267587012_10165813705855032_6465005238911365254_n-1536x875.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/267587012_10165813705855032_6465005238911365254_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268563218_10165813711735032_8737624210367283979_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077307" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268563218_10165813711735032_8737624210367283979_n-694x406.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="406" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268563218_10165813711735032_8737624210367283979_n-694x406.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268563218_10165813711735032_8737624210367283979_n-1280x749.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268563218_10165813711735032_8737624210367283979_n-768x450.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268563218_10165813711735032_8737624210367283979_n-1536x899.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268563218_10165813711735032_8737624210367283979_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269273361_10165813705905032_3811209318941348833_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077308" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269273361_10165813705905032_3811209318941348833_n-694x438.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269273361_10165813705905032_3811209318941348833_n-694x438.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269273361_10165813705905032_3811209318941348833_n-1280x807.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269273361_10165813705905032_3811209318941348833_n-768x484.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269273361_10165813705905032_3811209318941348833_n-1536x969.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269273361_10165813705905032_3811209318941348833_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲相片來源： <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/553511078046085/permalink/4977212165675932/">Facebook 群組「香港風景攝影會」</a></p><p>樓主指上述相片攝於南生圍空地，用了航拍機拍了兩天而成，由大約 6 時開始才能拍攝出日出地霧，地霧於 7 時半後便會漸漸消退。他對相片大感滿意，表示是在香港見過最美麗、最震撼的情景之一，十分滿足。</p><p>網民亦紛紛留言讚賞樓主的攝影技術和成果，大部分網民形容相片十分夢幻，完全不像香港，有如世外桃源般。亦有人稱「將香港影到意大利咁，師兄有料」、「好有耐心的等待，讓人感動的作品」，並指照片如畫般層次豐富，可媲美電影景，更以為是 Star War 的行星 Tatooine。有住在當地的網民感到驚訝，稱「住喺度都唔知靚成咁」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/fb-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077310" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/fb-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/fb-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/fb-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/fb-1.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/553511078046085/permalink/4977212165675932/">Facebook 群組「香港風景攝影會」</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
